%% Export : sequence_telemetry.png
sequenceDiagram
    participant ROS as rosbridge :9090
    participant SDK as RealRobot
    participant API as Backend FastAPI
    participant WS as WebSocket Manager
    participant UI as Frontend opérateur

    Note over ROS,SDK: Connexion WebSocket JSON persistante

    loop Flux temps réel
        ROS-->>SDK: /robot_pose ~10 Hz
        ROS-->>SDK: /robot_status ~2 Hz
        ROS-->>SDK: /scan_filter LiDAR ~25 Hz
        ROS-->>SDK: /detected_people_array ~2 Hz
        SDK->>API: callbacks mise à jour état
        API->>WS: broadcast JSON
        WS-->>UI: pose, status, lidar, people
        UI->>UI: re-render carte et barre statut
    end

    Note over UI: Commandes opérateur via REST,<br/>pas via ce flux WebSocket
